text.text:
SELECT 
  t.Id,
  t.Species,
  CASE 
    WHEN Id LIKE '%9%' THEN NULL
    ELSE [Petal.Width]
  END AS petal_width_mod,
  t1.mean_petal_w,
  t1.min_petal_w
FROM(
    SELECT
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY (SELECT NULL)) AS id,
        *
    FROM IrisRstudio
    ) AS t
--- Pegar tabla resumen
LEFT JOIN(
  SELECT
    Species,
    AVG(petal_width_mod) AS mean_petal_w,
    MIN(petal_width_mod) AS min_petal_w
  -- Cambio tabla
  FROM (
    SELECT 
      t.Id,
      t.Species,
      CASE 
        WHEN Id LIKE '%9%' THEN NULL
        ELSE [Petal.Width]
      END AS petal_width_mod
    FROM(
        SELECT
            ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY (SELECT NULL)) AS id,
            *
        FROM IrisRstudio
        ) AS t
    )
    --- Fin tabla
  GROUP BY Species --- resumen de la tabla
  ) AS t1 ON t.Species = t1.Species
